From 4c2e015785327a860487fe2bd08de1283547b8f1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Karsten Sperling <ksperling@apple.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Oct 2025 17:08:49 +1300
Subject: [PATCH] Ubus: Handle dispatching via a template to avoid boilerplate
 parsing code.

Also get rid of the remaining statics / globals in UbusServer.
Fix uninitialized otLinkModeConfig in "setmode" handler.
---
 src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.cpp     | 1577 ++++++++++++-------------------
 src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.hpp     |  982 ++-----------------
 src/openwrt/ubus/ubus_utils.hpp |  117 +++
 3 files changed, 799 insertions(+), 1877 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/openwrt/ubus/ubus_utils.hpp

diff --git a/src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.cpp b/src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.cpp
index a18af82a..78860e40 100644
--- a/src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.cpp
+++ b/src/openwrt/ubus/otubus.cpp
